summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 221E, page 8 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 1-4 incl., Block 6, Lots 1-10 incl., Block 5, all in Kenwood Add., located on west side of 35th Ave. N.E. from E. 135th St. to E. 140th St., from Single Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone to Duplex Residence Medium Density (RD 7200) Zone.
